msgstr "動詞"

#: ../../W/warlording.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from the Usenet group :samp:`alt.fan.warlord`\\] The act of excoriating a "
"bloated, ugly, or derivative :ref:`sig-block`\\. Common grounds for "
"warlording include the presence of a signature rendered in a :ref:`BUAF`\\, "
"over-used or cliched :ref:`sig-quote`\\s, ugly :ref:`ASCII-art`\\, or simply"
" excessive size. The original ‘Warlord’ was a :ref:`B1FF`\\-like "
":ref:`newbie` c.1991 who featured in his sig a particularly large and "
"obnoxious ASCII graphic resembling the sword of Conan the Barbarian in the "
"1981 John Milius movie; the group name :samp:`alt.fan.warlord` was sarcasm, "
"and the characteristic mode of warlording is devastatingly sarcastic praise."
" See also :ref:`McQuary-limit`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Usenetグループ\\ :samp:`alt.fan.warlord`\\ から] 膨れ上がった、醜い、あるいは独創性のない\\ "
":ref:`sig-block`\\ を糾弾する行為。warlordingの一般的な根拠には、\\ :ref:`BUAF`\\ "
"で描かれた署名の存在、使い古されたあるいは陳腐な\\ :ref:`sig-quote`\\ 、醜い\\ :ref:`ASCII-art`\\ "
"、あるいは単に過剰なサイズが含まれる。元祖の‘Warlord’は1991年頃の\\ :ref:`B1FF`\\ 風の\\ :ref:`newbie`\\"
" で、1981年のJohn Miliusの映画の蛮人コナンの剣に似た、特に大きくて目障りなASCIIグラフィックを署名に載せていた。グループ名\\ "
":samp:`alt.fan.warlord`\\ は皮肉であり、warlordingの特徴的な様式は、壊滅的に皮肉な称賛である。\\ "
":ref:`McQuary-limit`\\ も参照。"
